name: Rahul Kothari
description: Rahul is currently a Product Manager at Aztec, where he focuses on shipping the first ever privacy focussed decentralized L2. He has led key strategic initiatives and also owns the Aztec Sandbox and Devnet. Previously Rahul was a smart contract engineer at Aztec building the L2, worked at Reddit's Crypto team, onboarding 30M people and at Ethereum Foundation and bluesky.
